# sakura_cloudhsm_license (Resource)

Manages a CloudHSM License.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "sakura_cloudhsm_license" "foobar" {
  name = "foobar"
  description = "foobar description"
  tags = ["terraform"]
}
```

## Schema

### Required

- `name` (String) The name of the CloudHSM License.

### Optional

- `description` (String) The description of the CloudHSM License. The length of this value must be in the range [`1`-`512`]
- `tags` (Set of String) The tags of the CloudHSM License.
- `timeouts` (Attributes) (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--timeouts))
- `zone` (String) The zone of the CloudHSM License. This must be one of [`is1b`/`tk1a`]

### Read-Only

- `id` (String) The ID of the CloudHSM License.
- `modified_at` (String) The modification date of the CloudHSM License
